name: the future is...
description: October 2018, they say that the future will be private.  His eyes and mouth say something different.  The future is private. VS The privacy is dead.  The future is private and decentralized  This artwork was conceived using Facebook's Spark AR Tool, Was published as Instagram Filter, and now is available to be collected at Hic et Nunc.
